        <item>
            <title>Bang &#038; Olufsen 复修 70 年代转盘唱机，索价 27 万元、全球限量 10 部</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/bno-turntable/mobile-music/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bno-turntable</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/bno-turntable/mobile-music/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 06:35:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动音乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Bang & Olufsen]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Saint Laurent]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295855</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Bang &amp; Olufsen 联手 Saint Laurent 复刻经典，推出 Bang &amp; Olufsen Beogram 4000c Saint Laurent Rive Droite Edition 黑胶碟唱机，定价 35,000 美元（约港币 27.2 万元）。这款 1970 年代的传奇硬件经手工精选修复，搭载新世代唱头与前置放大器，外壳选用珍贵的 Ziricote 木材，全球限量仅 10 部。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295859" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen1-683x580.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen1-683x580.jpg 683w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen1.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 683px" /></p><p>Bang &amp; Olufsen 最新推出的 Beogram 4000c Saint Laurent Rive Droite Edition 复古设计之中加入现代技术。这款唱盘由 1970 年代的原装机型精心修复而成，在 Saint Laurent 创意总监 Anthony Vaccarello 监督下，外观以高雅的 Ziricote 木盒呈现，并融入铝质细节，彰显独特品味。产品保留原有经典设计，更升级音质，搭载新世代唱头与前置放大器，迎合现代发烧友需求。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>音质升级亦不遑多让，满足当代乐迷的挑剔耳朵。据外媒披露，Bang &amp; Olufsen 早于 2020 年曾修复 95 部 Beogram 4000c，索价美元 11,000 元（约港币 85,481 元）仍火速售罄。今次将于 Saint Laurent Rive Droite 巴黎、洛杉矶门店及线上平台登场，令人拭目以待。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-16dba41 r-1adg3ll r-1b5gpbm r-a8ghvy" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">此款唱盘定价 27.2 万元，瞄准高端收藏家及音响爱好者市场。Bang &amp; Olufsen 选择修复原装硬件而非全新制造，既保留复古情怀，又提升技术规格，与市场上追求创新的品牌形成鲜明对比。</span></span>限量发售料将引发抢购热潮，或启发品牌进一步探索联名可能。</div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen4-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen4-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bangolufsen4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="http://theverge.com/news/624832/bang-olufsen-saint-laurent-beogram-4000c-turntable">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.techradar.com/audio/turntables/bang-and-olufsens-latest-reworked-turntable-is-a-masterpiece-of-retro-revival-in-a-breathtaking-wooden-presentation-box">Tech Radar</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/bno-turntable/mobile-music/">Bang &#038; Olufsen 复修 70 年代转盘唱机，索价 27 万元、全球限量 10 部</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
