        <item>
            <title>JR「E10 系」新干线列车 2030 年登场，从设计上著重行车安全、最高时速保持 320 公里</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/jr-e10/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jr-e10</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/jr-e10/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 05:40:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295874</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>JR 东日本宣布开发东北新干线新一代列车「E10 系」，预计首批列车将于 2027 年秋季完工，并计划 2030 年度投入商业营运。此列车将取代现有的「E2 系」及「E5 系」，最高时速维持每小时 320 公里，并采用东北地区山脉为灵感的绿色设计。列车提升安全性能，并配备商务旅客所需的设施。</p><p>「E10 系」由英国设计公司 Tangerine Design 操刀，外观以浅绿与深绿双色呈现，灵感源自东北山脉自然景观。列车为 10 节编组，最高时速达 320 公里每小时。「E10 系」在安全设计上精益求精，采用「ALFA-X」先进技术。刹车距离较「E5 系」缩减 15%，并引入减震器以抑制地震时的左右摇晃，有效降低列车的脱轨风险，确保乘客在突发情况下的安全，充分回应日本地震频发的环境挑战。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0213-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0213-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0213.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0214-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0214-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0214.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>为满足商务需求，部分车厢采用每排 4 座的宽敞布局，所有座位配备电源插座及 USB 充电。根据 NHK 报导，列车内设 TRAIN DESK 工作区，座椅间加装隔板，提升私隐及舒适度。然而首批「E10 系」将取消豪华「Gran Class」舱位，引发关注。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0217-546x580.jpg" alt="" width="546" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0217-546x580.jpg 546w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0217.jpg 847w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 546px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲设有「TRAIN DESK」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0215-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0215-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/rpn20250304hsor0215.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲座椅间有隔板</p><p>网民对「E10 系」看法不一，不少人关注其定位，认为未完全展现次世代潜力。网民 @Sliversmith 认为：「因札幌延伸未定，320 公里时速似妥协，若未来需 360 公里新车，E10 或沦为过渡品。」</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">新干线のE10､札幌延伸の目処が立たないせいで320km/hまでで抑えられてるが､いざ札幌延伸が决まると360km/hの新型が求められ､早々に要らない子扱いになりそうな予感<br />
蒸気机関车のE10は典型的な不遇车だったが､新干线の方は不遇车回避できるだろうか</p><p>— itsuki hajime (@Sliversmith) <a href="https://twitter.com/Sliversmith/status/1896918503451746383?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 4, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOUC221CW0S5A220C2000000/">日本经济新闻</a>、<a href="https://news.railway-pressnet.com/archives/73613">News.Railway</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/jr-e10/life-tech/travel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>消防新设电动车灭火工具，呼吁市民勿自行扑灭电动车火警</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/fireman-new-tools-for-electric-car-fire/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fireman-new-tools-for-electric-car-fire</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/06/fireman-new-tools-for-electric-car-fire/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 05:35:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295850</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港消防处宣布引入电动车灭火救援工具，以应对日益增加的电动车火警事故。据统计，2024 年涉及电动车的交通意外及火警达 48 宗，较前年激增 92%。消防处强调，电动车起火时，锂电池可能因高温引发「热失控」，火势迅速扩散并伴有爆炸风险，故呼吁市民切勿自行救火，应即时撤离并报警求助。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030613201-694x325.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="325" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030613201-694x325.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030613201.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲应急插头可防止电动车无故移动</p><p>电动车火警因锂电池结构特殊，救援难度较传统汽油车为高。助理消防区长文家平指出，电池多藏于车底并有坚固外壳保护，单靠外围射水难以直接灭火。国际研究显示，处理此类火警或需耗时 4 小时及 15 万公升水。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295895" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_4_l_20-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_4_l_20-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_4_l_20.jpg 1275w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲应急插头为电动车模拟充电状态</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295915" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481454694_1046063887-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481454694_1046063887-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481454694_1046063887.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲防止车辆在突然行驶，对救援人员产生危险</p><p>消防处新引入的工具，包括电动车应急插头、灭火毡及电池灭火系统，显著提升效率。据近期训练及行动数据，消防人员平均只需 2 小时及 1 万 5 千公升水，便可稳定电池温度，成效远超传统方法。为进一步提升救援能力，消防处已于各分区配备相关设备，并加强人员训练。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295916" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481989947_1046063920-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481989947_1046063920-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481989947_1046063920.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲电动车辆灭火毡以窒息法辅助灭火，防止火势、有毒气体及浓烟扩散</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295896" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_3_l_20-694x443.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="443" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_3_l_20-694x443.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/mfile_1794480_3_l_20.jpg 1270w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲电池灭火系统</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295917" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481906043_1046063870-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481906043_1046063870-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481906043_1046063870.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲瞬间刺穿电池外壳并直接注水，迅速为电池降温</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295913" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481951080_1046063850-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481951080_1046063850-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481951080_1046063850.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲高压喷雾喉笔可产生水雾，覆盖电动车底的电池起火位置，迅速降温</p><p>消防处提醒驾驶者，若发现电池系统发出警示、异常气味或烟雾，应立即停车撤离，并马上报警求助。即使附近有水源，亦不建议自行灭火，因锂电池燃烧释放的气体及火焰极具危险性。随著电动车数量持续上升，相关火警事故或仍会增加，预料消防处将持续提升设备及应急策略。同时市民对电动车风险的认知亦需提升，未来或见更多公众教育活动，防患于未然。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1794480-20250306.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
